171 A.3d 1253 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DAVID ARISTE, A/K/A D-BRIM, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-185 Sept. Term 2017

079286 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001892-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
